        <div class="message-card orange-outline">
          <div class="timing-label">⏰ 24-Hour Reminder</div>
          <div class="timing-desc">Sent 24 hours before appointment</div>
          <div class="input-group">
            <label class="input-label">Message</label>
            <textarea id="reminder-24h" style="min-height:110px">Hi {{first_name}}! Just a reminder that your HomeUp consultation is tomorrow 📆

🕐 {{appt_time}} with {{agent_name}}

Need to reschedule? No worries: {{reschedule_link}}</textarea>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="message-card orange-outline">
          <div class="timing-label">🔔 1-Hour Reminder</div>
          <div class="timing-desc">Sent 1 hour before appointment</div>
          <div class="input-group">
            <label class="input-label">Message</label>
            <textarea id="reminder-1h" style="min-height:110px">Hey {{first_name}}! Your call with {{agent_name}} is in 1 hour ⏱

Join here: {{meeting_link}}

See you soon! 👋</textarea>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="message-card orange-outline">
          <div class="timing-label">💌 Post-Appointment Follow-Up</div>
          <div class="timing-desc">Sent 2 hours after appointment</div>
          <div class="input-group">
            <label class="input-label">Message</label>
            <textarea id="reminder-post" style="min-height:110px">Hi {{first_name}}! It was great chatting with you today 😊

We'll be sending over some options based on what we discussed. In the meantime, feel free to reply here with any questions!

— {{agent_name}}, HomeUp</textarea>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- INSTRUCTIONS -->
    <section id="instructions" class="section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="orange-badge">Automated · Post-booking</div>
        <div class="section-title">Appointment Instructions</div>
        <div class="section-desc">Prep notes and instructions sent to leads after they book — what to expect, what to bring, and how to join.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="message-card orange-outline">
        <div class="input-group">
          <label class="input-label">Instructions Message</label>
          <textarea id="appt-instructions" style="min-height:180px">Hi {{first_name}}! Here's what to expect from your HomeUp consultation 📋

✅ What we'll cover:
