Your call is with {{agent_name}} on {{appt_date}} at {{appt_time}}.
📞 Join here: {{meeting_link}}

We're excited to help you find the one! 🏡</textarea>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FOLLOW-UPS -->
    <section id="followups" class="section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="orange-badge">Automated · No-Reply Re-engagement</div>
        <div class="section-title">Follow-Up Sequence</div>
        <div class="section-desc">Sent to leads who haven't replied. Timed at 7, 30, and 90 days after initial contact.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="var-hint">💡 Available variables:</div>
      <div class="variable-chips" style="margin-bottom:20px">
        <span class="var-chip" onclick="copyVar(this)">{{first_name}}</span>
        <span class="var-chip" onclick="copyVar(this)">{{booking_link}}</span>
        <span class="var-chip" onclick="copyVar(this)">{{agent_name}}</span>
      </div>

      <div class="timing-grid">
        <div class="timing-card">
          <div class="timing-label">Day 7</div>
          <div class="timing-desc">First re-engagement. Keep it warm and low-pressure.</div>
          <div class="input-group">
            <label class="input-label">Message</label>
            <textarea style="min-height:140px">Hey {{first_name}}! 👋

Just checking in — we noticed you hadn't had a chance to book yet.

No rush at all, but when you're ready, we'd love to help you explore your options 🏠

